45:35.767 --> 45:39.805
Now you are one of us, Michael.

45:45.877 --> 45:47.445
Self protection, huh?

45:47.478 --> 45:49.147
I understand that.

45:49.180 --> 45:51.249
We all need protection today.

45:51.282 --> 45:53.284
Am I right or am I right?

45:53.919 --> 45:55.053
Now this baby...

45:55.086 --> 45:58.256
this here is The
Terminator of all handguns.

45:58.289 --> 46:01.860
It'll blow a hole so big in a
man, you gonna see Alaska, baby.

46:05.296 --> 46:08.299
And ain't nobody getting up
after you use that cannon.

46:11.803 --> 46:15.006
