46:28.353 --> 46:31.122
Yeah...you got the look
of a stone cold killa'.

46:32.123 --> 46:34.025
I think I made a big mistake.

46:34.059 --> 46:35.226
Oh, baby...

46:35.260 --> 46:37.428
