46:56.514 --> 46:58.516
You can keep the cash you find.

46:58.549 --> 47:00.886
Three mill, maybe five.

47:00.919 --> 47:02.921
Now you are one of us, Michael.

47:05.356 --> 47:07.358
So who died and left you king?

47:07.926 --> 47:09.027
