with Sara's father.

47:18.937 --> 47:22.140
I see. What kind of deal?

47:22.173 --> 47:24.509
Relax, Jerry.
No strings attached.

47:24.542 --> 47:27.412
The important thing is that the
company is once again healthy.

47:27.445 --> 47:30.015
Well Mike, I don't want to rain
on your parade but there are

47:30.048 --> 47:33.418
