47:37.956 --> 47:40.258
Just don't let him...

47:40.291 --> 47:42.060
Ha ha ha! Wow!

47:42.093 --> 47:45.096
This is a great view.

47:45.130 --> 47:46.464
Maybe I should learn to
speak Russian

47:46.497 --> 47:48.499
so I can properly thank him.

47:48.967 --> 47:49.968
Them.

47:50.868 --> 47:51.869
Them?

47:53.638 --> 47:55.506
Oh, it's a them now.

47:56.074 --> 47:57.508
What happened to her father?

47:57.542 --> 47:59.144
He has partners, Jerry.

47:59.177 --> 48:02.380
Mm..hm...Russian partners?

48:03.581 --> 48:06.184
Don't get me wrong. Good
Russians make good partners.

48:06.217 --> 48:08.153
But bad Russians...

48:08.186 --> 48:11.389
Bad Russians will leave us at
the bottom of the harbor.

48:11.422 --> 48:14.092
What are you worried about?
You know how to swim.

48:14.125 --> 48:17.228
Not with a hundred pound
weight cemented to my feet.

48:17.895 --> 48:21.032
Then let's hope it
doesn't come to that.

48:21.066 --> 48:23.068
Oh yeah, let's hope...

48:24.169 --> 48:29.507
Well, maybe, just maybe,
this will all be worth it.

48:31.576 --> 48:33.011
Hey...

48:33.044 --> 48:35.613
I'm gonna need
a new wardrobe.

48:35.646 --> 48:38.149
Yes you are, Jerry.
Yes you are.

48:38.183 --> 48:40.185
Ha ha! Excellent.

50:37.768 --> 50:39.370
Jerry!

50:46.111 --> 50:48.079
What are you doing?

50:48.113 --> 50:50.115
It's your fiancée.

51:13.738 --> 51:15.740
Jerry!

52:10.661 --> 52:13.198
9-1-1, please state the
nature of your emergency.

52:13.231 --> 52:14.832
My fiancée, she's...

52:14.865 --> 52:16.867
Please state your emergency.

52:17.134 --> 52:18.836
She's--she has
rabies or something

52:18.869 --> 52:20.671
Sir, please state your emergency.

52:20.705 --> 52:21.772
She's trying to kill me.

52:21.806 --> 52:23.274
Who is trying to kill you, sir?

52:23.308 --> 52:24.442
My fiancée!

52:24.475 --> 52:26.611
In what way is she
trying to kill you, sir?

52:28.413 --> 52:29.847
She's trying to
bite me to death.

52:29.880 --> 52:33.184
Sir, we have had an overload
of prank calls tonight.

52:33.218 --> 52:35.820
Calling 911 as
a joke is a crime.

52:35.853 --> 52:37.054
It is a felony.

52:37.087 --> 52:39.424
I have two fingers and my big
toe in the freezer

52:39.457 --> 52:41.559
to prove to you
this is no damn joke!

52:41.592 --> 52:42.760
What was that?

52:42.793 --> 52:43.861
She's trying to get in.

52:45.530 --> 52:46.797
Where are you now?

52:47.265 --> 52:48.633
I'm locked in the bathroom.

52:48.666 --> 52:50.235
Sir, listen to me...

52:50.268 --> 52:52.837
We have been inundated
tonight with strange calls.

52:52.870 --> 52:55.873
But I will have a patrol car
to you as soon as possible.

52:56.674 --> 52:59.910
What is your address?

52:59.944 --> 53:02.680
33430 Rustic Canyon Drive

53:02.713 --> 53:05.550
Do not open that door
until the police arrive.

53:05.583 --> 53:07.618
Do you understand?

53:07.652 --> 53:08.619
Do you understand?!

53:08.653 --> 53:09.654
I'm not an idiot!

53:14.825 --> 53:17.628
1 Adam 4, 1 Adam 4 do you copy?

53:20.431 --> 53:23.534
Adam 4, this is
Dispatch. Do you copy?

53:24.469 --> 53:28.273
Damn. Is she trying to
kill my buzz? Really?

53:28.306 --> 53:32.910
1 Adam 4, this is
Dispatch. Do you copy?

53:33.811 --> 53:36.947
Better answer her.
She'll never leave us alone.

53:40.851 --> 53:45.790
Uh...10-4 Dispatch.
We copy. Loud and clear.

53:46.824 --> 53:49.894
Be advised, we have a
domestic disturbance at

53:49.927 --> 53:53.831
33430 Rustic Canyon Road.

53:54.699 --> 53:55.966
No, dispatch.

53:56.000 --> 53:58.303
Contact Ben.
That's his patrol.

53:59.504 --> 54:01.606
Don't think we
haven't been trying.

54:01.639 --> 54:04.609
Ben hasn't answered
and has not called in.

54:05.843 --> 54:08.012
He's probably
sleeping one off.

54:09.314 --> 54:10.715
Again?

54:12.249 --> 54:15.520
Uh, 10-4 Dispatch.
We are on our way.

54:16.321 --> 54:17.855
Please be advised...

54:17.888 --> 54:21.792
Vic says his fiancée is
trying to bite him to death.

54:21.826 --> 54:24.028
He's locked himself
in the bathroom.

54:25.630 --> 54:27.632
Ha ha! Say it again?

54:28.566 --> 54:33.938
Vic says his fiancée is
trying to bite him to death.

54:33.971 --> 54:36.741
He's locked himself
in the bathroom.

54:36.774 --> 54:40.778
He says she's bitten off
two of his fingers and a toe.

54:42.413 --> 54:44.515
10-4 Dispatch.

54:44.549 --> 54:46.651
We'll muzzle her if needed.

54:46.684 --> 54:48.686
Over and out.

54:49.587 --> 54:52.990
That must be one angry fiancée.

54:53.858 --> 54:54.692
Now...

54:54.725 --> 54:56.561
what would you do...

54:56.594 --> 54:58.896
if your fiancée no less...

54:58.929 --> 55:00.931
bit off your toe?

55:01.298 --> 55:03.300
You know what I'd do.

55:04.369 --> 55:05.736
Exactly.

55:06.571 --> 55:07.972
Let's not hurry this.

55:08.005 --> 55:10.007
If this guy can't take
care of his woman...

55:12.343 --> 55:13.944
Exactly.

55:13.978 --> 55:16.647
I say we fire up one more.

55:16.681 --> 55:19.517
It'll give us better perspective

55:19.550 --> 55:21.886
of the overall situation

55:21.919 --> 55:23.488
when we get there.

55:23.521 --> 55:24.989
Exactly.

55:25.423 --> 55:28.559
Besides, he's locked
himself in the bathroom.

55:37.568 --> 55:38.769
In the old country...

55:39.670 --> 55:40.971
...we'd cut off
your hands and feet

55:41.005 --> 55:44.008
and leave you in
the woods with the wolves.

55:44.041 --> 55:46.977
That way you'd still be
alive when they devoured you.

55:47.011 --> 55:48.579
That's the old way.

55:49.647 --> 55:53.984
Today, we have law to
take care of pound of flesh.

55:54.018 --> 55:55.420
Most of the time.

55:55.453 --> 55:57.888
Yes. Most of the time.

55:57.922 --> 55:58.956
But...

55:58.989 --> 56:01.859
Even in this country
we know how to make you pay.

56:01.892 --> 56:03.861
You disappointed us, Michael.

56:03.894 --> 56:06.363
You invested our money
without including us.

56:06.397 --> 56:07.398
Your money?

56:07.432 --> 56:08.433
Of course.

56:08.466 --> 56:10.401
Who's money did
you think it was?

56:10.435 --> 56:12.336
You said, "keep the cash".

56:12.369 --> 56:13.337
Yes.

56:13.370 --> 56:15.139
But it is not your cash.

56:15.806 --> 56:21.646
We could not explain money,
so you were our bank, Michael.

56:21.679 --> 56:23.581
But make no mistake...

56:23.614 --> 56:24.949
It's our cash.

56:24.982 --> 56:27.518
You truly didn't think
the money was yours?

56:28.653 --> 56:30.821
Sometimes in this country
you people have more

56:30.855 --> 56:32.122
balls than brains.

56:32.156 --> 56:34.459
Which brings us
back to our problem.

56:34.492 --> 56:36.126
We want our money.

56:36.160 --> 56:38.896
There is no actual money.

56:38.929 --> 56:40.931
As you said,
the money's invested.

56:40.965 --> 56:44.001
You invested our
money without including us.

56:45.570 --> 56:47.838
You said, "keep the cash"!

56:47.872 --> 56:51.075
Don't play tough guy
with us, Michael.

56:51.108 --> 56:53.444
Maybe you think
you are tough guy

56:53.478 --> 56:55.580
and we are dumb immigrants.

56:55.613 --> 56:58.983
One week. We want our money.

56:59.016 --> 57:01.986
One week, Michael. No more.

57:02.019 --> 57:07.625
Or you will wake up and find
your big balls in your mouth.

57:22.740 --> 57:24.809
Well, welcome back Kotter.

57:24.842 --> 57:26.777
You know, I always
thought I'd see you again.

57:26.811 --> 57:27.945
You had that look.

57:27.978 --> 57:28.879
What look?

57:29.446 --> 57:31.782
The look of a killa'.
Hungry for action.

57:31.816 --> 57:33.884
Or maybe just desperate.

57:33.918 --> 57:35.920
No, not you.

57:36.887 --> 57:39.757
