alert within the hour.

01:00:45.676 --> 01:00:47.144
What gives?

01:00:47.177 --> 01:00:48.979
Need to know basis.

01:00:49.013 --> 01:00:52.016
We'll get briefed after all
cars return to Headquarters.

01:00:53.050 --> 01:00:54.985
What? We're being recalled?

01:00:55.019 --> 01:00:56.286
That's a big 10-4.

01:00:56.320 --> 01:01:00.024
