01:01:06.030 --> 01:01:08.032
Now, what is up with that?

01:01:11.035 --> 01:01:13.037
Beats the hell out of me.

01:01:14.839 --> 01:01:16.373
But the question is...

01:01:16.406 --> 01:01:19.076
Do we still go
up to Rustic Canyon?

01:01:19.810 --> 01:01:22.412
Well, if we gun it...

01:01:22.446 --> 01:01:24.782
I mean, if we really gun it...

01:01:24.815 --> 01:01:26.817
We're only about
ten minutes away.

01:01:28.118 --> 01:01:30.020
And I, for one...

01:01:30.054 --> 01:01:33.057
want to see that killer fiancée.

01:01:33.991 --> 01:01:35.993
I want to see
the ball-less wonder.

01:01:41.698 --> 01:01:43.133
I say we go for it.

01:01:43.167 --> 01:01:44.301
I'm with you!

01:01:44.334 --> 01:01:46.336
Well then, let's do it!

01:04:30.234 --> 01:04:33.237
I'll do the heavy lifting.
You do the cleanup.

01:04:39.643 --> 01:04:41.411
Thornton, you're not on the list

01:04:42.279 --> 01:04:44.314
What about now?
