01:05:22.552 --> 01:05:24.154
Face it, Michael.

01:05:24.188 --> 01:05:26.323
She's never coming back to you.

01:05:28.325 --> 01:05:31.028
And why didn't she
break through the windows?

01:05:37.667 --> 01:05:40.670
Because she can't
stand her own reflection.

01:05:41.972 --> 01:05:44.208
So what's a guy
like you gonna do?

01:05:48.178 --> 01:05:50.180
I'm gonna kill that bitch.

01:05:56.220 --> 01:05:57.354
Oh yeah.

01:06:04.028 --> 01:06:06.330
Fiancée my ass.

01:07:18.202 --> 01:07:19.636
Michael?

01:09:51.555 --> 01:09:54.558
Out of sight, out of mind.

01:10:56.353 --> 01:10:58.688
Buck up, Bucko.

01:11:51.875 --> 01:11:54.711
Well, well, well.
What a weekend!

