People apparently just went
crack crazy this weekend!

01:12:10.560 --> 01:12:12.596
That is bad news. And..?

01:12:12.629 --> 01:12:13.497
And what?

01:12:13.530 --> 01:12:14.898
And what about
the Bigfoot rumor?

01:12:14.931 --> 01:12:16.299
Oh! So you heard?

01:12:16.332 --> 01:12:18.334
It's all anyone is talking about.

01:12:18.368 --> 01:12:20.904
For those of you who were living
under a rock or in a cave this

01:12:20.937 --> 01:12:24.474
weekend, the rumor is...
They found Bigfoot!

01:12:24.508 --> 01:12:25.842
Please go on.

01:12:25.875 --> 01:12:27.977
The rumor is not only that they
found Bigfoot but they found

01:12:28.011 --> 01:12:31.047
him dead in the middle of the road with a
 tire iron sticking through his chest.

01:12:31.080 --> 01:12:36.753
That's exactly what I'm hearing. They say 
the body measured nine to ten feet tall!

01:12:36.786 --> 01:12:40.757
But the authorities aren't talking.
They will neither confirm nor deny!

01:12:40.790 --> 01:12:45.429
Obviously they will be housed with Area
51 and all the little green aliens.

01:12:45.462 --> 01:12:47.397
Ha ha! You are correct, sir!

01:12:47.431 --> 01:12:48.364
I am indeed.

01:12:48.398 --> 01:12:50.400
Any other local news of interest?

01:12:50.434 --> 01:12:55.772
Local doctors were able to successfully
re-attach two fingers, a thumb, and a big toe

01:12:55.805 --> 01:12:59.409
to a man who must have thrown
himself in front of a lawn mower.

01:12:59.443 --> 01:13:02.779
You know, some guys will do
anything to get out of taking out the trash.

01:13:02.812 --> 01:13:06.583
Wow! A big toe!
Amazing what science can do.

01:13:06.616 --> 01:13:08.685
Amazing, amazing, amazing it is.

01:13:08.718 --> 01:13:10.119
That's one lucky fellow.

01:13:10.153 --> 01:13:12.055
Yes he is, he is indeed.

01:13:12.088 --> 01:13:14.891
Now to warm up our night...
here's some summer music.

01:13:46.456 --> 01:13:50.126
You can imagine how
skeptical people are right now.

01:13:50.994 --> 01:13:52.829
Official word to be
released is that the

01:13:52.862 --> 01:13:55.599
county water supply
was contaminated.

01:13:56.165 --> 01:13:58.167
With LSD.

01:13:59.503 --> 01:14:01.605
Do you think I did this to myself?

01:14:01.638 --> 01:14:03.607
Well, stranger things have
happened to people under

01:14:03.640 --> 01:14:05.642
the influence of hallucinogens.

01:14:06.543 --> 01:14:08.411
But I digress --

01:14:08.444 --> 01:14:11.815
The only reason we agreed to
this interview is you maintain

01:14:11.848 --> 01:14:14.851
you have proof of
what you say happened...

01:14:15.451 --> 01:14:16.586
I mean...

01:14:16.620 --> 01:14:21.090
Even you have to admit your
story is fanciful and...

01:14:21.124 --> 01:14:22.726
quite difficult to believe.

01:14:22.759 --> 01:14:24.127
Yes.

01:14:24.160 --> 01:14:26.530
I find it quite
difficult to believe.

01:14:27.463 --> 01:14:29.465
But you say you have proof.

01:14:30.700 --> 01:14:32.468
We need to see it, Michael.

01:14:32.502 --> 01:14:34.838
When my Fiancée...

01:14:34.871 --> 01:14:36.172
She bit me.

01:14:36.205 --> 01:14:39.509
She bit me many many times.

01:14:39.543 --> 01:14:43.012
It was inevitable that her
blood would mix with mine.

01:14:44.848 --> 01:14:47.751
I can feel the changes.

01:14:47.784 --> 01:14:52.155
That's all well and good but
we need to see actual proof!

01:14:52.789 --> 01:14:54.791
Oh, I'm going
to show you proof.

01:14:55.992 --> 01:15:00.129
I'm going to show you all
the proof you will ever...

01:15:01.130 --> 01:15:03.132
...need.

